[
  {
    "startTime": 1.334,
    "endTime": 2.936,
    "text": "No one is noticing this?!?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.936,
    "endTime": 3.937,
    "text": "These kids are buggin out,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.937,
    "endTime": 5.538,
    "text": "because once I would've seen the red sh*t…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.538,
    "endTime": 6.272,
    "text": "I'm out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.272,
    "endTime": 7.24,
    "text": "Hi, I'm Alejandro."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.24,
    "endTime": 7.574,
    "text": "Chris."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.574,
    "endTime": 7.941,
    "text": "Taylor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.941,
    "endTime": 8.341,
    "text": "Kaley."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.341,
    "endTime": 8.741999999999999,
    "text": "Andy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.742,
    "endTime": 9.509,
    "text": "And I've never seen"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.509,
    "endTime": 9.943,
    "text": "never seen"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.943,
    "endTime": 11.211,
    "text": "never seen 'Jaws.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.945,
    "endTime": 14.047,
    "text": "'Jaws' is about people, they're on a beach"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.047,
    "endTime": 16.082,
    "text": "there's a lot of taco meat, lot of chest hair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.082,
    "endTime": 17.417,
    "text": "A big ass shark..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.417,
    "endTime": 19.085,
    "text": "I don't know if it's mutated or like..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.085,
    "endTime": 19.919,
    "text": "possessed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.919,
    "endTime": 21.287,
    "text": "Jaws goes like that or whatever…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.287,
    "endTime": 23.622,
    "text": "He has massive... jaws!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.623,
    "endTime": 26.292,
    "text": "Yeah, I think it's just about people dying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.292,
    "endTime": 27.961000000000002,
    "text": "I'm ready to swim, Jim!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.961,
    "endTime": 30.363,
    "text": "(Offscreen) I'm totally messing with you. That's not in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.363,
    "endTime": 32.399,
    "text": "I know you've got a lot of problems downtown, but…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.099,
    "endTime": 34.733,
    "text": "Oh, this is an old movie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.734,
    "endTime": 36.469,
    "text": "Everyone's tan. Where is this, the Jersey Shore?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.469,
    "endTime": 39.039,
    "text": "Also, this man's face is far too close to the camera."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.806,
    "endTime": 41.574,
    "text": "Ah, sh*t… Awwww..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.574,
    "endTime": 43.143,
    "text": "Tricked me. Thought she got eaten."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.209,
    "endTime": 45.478,
    "text": "These young kids horsin' around!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.88,
    "endTime": 48.548,
    "text": "This is like the little boy who cried wolf."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.548,
    "endTime": 49.983000000000004,
    "text": "It's really going to happen this time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.985,
    "endTime": 53.053,
    "text": "Oh, is that the shark?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.053,
    "endTime": 54.888,
    "text": "Ok, here's the classic music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.954,
    "endTime": 58.792,
    "text": "Ok, we're seeing the shark's POV. We're seeing legs…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.792,
    "endTime": 61.061,
    "text": "They look delicious to the shark."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.061,
    "endTime": 62.228,
    "text": "Uh-oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.228,
    "endTime": 64.964,
    "text": "There's someone swimming…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.964,
    "endTime": 66.032,
    "text": "♪ (singing Jaws Theme) ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.801,
    "endTime": 68.868,
    "text": "Is that it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.971,
    "endTime": 74.641,
    "text": "Oh shit, he really bit her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.641,
    "endTime": 75.80900000000001,
    "text": "That's a lot of blood."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.809,
    "endTime": 76.843,
    "text": "Blood! Blood everywhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.843,
    "endTime": 77.744,
    "text": "There's blood everywhere!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.744,
    "endTime": 79.045,
    "text": "Is that really how shark attacks happen?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.045,
    "endTime": 81.714,
    "text": "That definitely like doesn't happen, just 'blurb.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.714,
    "endTime": 83.083,
    "text": "No one is noticing this?!?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.083,
    "endTime": 84.35,
    "text": "Yeah, these kids are buggin out,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.35,
    "endTime": 85.985,
    "text": "because once I would've seen the red sh*t…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.985,
    "endTime": 86.92,
    "text": "I'm out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.92,
    "endTime": 86.986,
    "text": "Shark's have 300 teeth. You only have 34."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.588,
    "endTime": 90.122,
    "text": "They're not going very fast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.123,
    "endTime": 92.42500000000001,
    "text": "They're kind of like,  'Oh no….'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.229,
    "endTime": 98.765,
    "text": "Ah, shit! She can't find her kid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.966,
    "endTime": 101.401,
    "text": "Where's Jimmy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.401,
    "endTime": 102.301,
    "text": "That is sad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.837,
    "endTime": 104.83800000000001,
    "text": "Ewwww."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.838,
    "endTime": 107.841,
    "text": "Oh my god, no! This is worse than the shark!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.841,
    "endTime": 109.208,
    "text": "Go on, stop it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.209,
    "endTime": 111.211,
    "text": "That's not how you get people's attention."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.211,
    "endTime": 114.013,
    "text": "I'll catch this bird for you, but it ain't going to be easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.013,
    "endTime": 115.548,
    "text": "I can't understand him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.548,
    "endTime": 117.884,
    "text": "Sounds Australian? British possibly?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.884,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "Seeking… tenderizing…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 121.988,
    "text": "He doesn't have good manners."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.988,
    "endTime": 123.123,
    "text": "He's talking with his mouth full."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.123,
    "endTime": 124.19,
    "text": "I don't trust him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.19,
    "endTime": 125.291,
    "text": "That man was born on a boat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.291,
    "endTime": 126.059,
    "text": "You can just tell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.059,
    "endTime": 128.394,
    "text": "I thought the same thing I thought when the movie began…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.461,
    "endTime": 129.863,
    "text": "He ain't sh*t"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.863,
    "endTime": 133.166,
    "text": "Come on down and chum some of this sh*t!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.166,
    "endTime": 133.9,
    "text": "Huh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.9,
    "endTime": 135.034,
    "text": "Holy shit!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.034,
    "endTime": 137.837,
    "text": "The guy on the boat literally just stood up and did nothing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.872,
    "endTime": 139.305,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.305,
    "endTime": 141.741,
    "text": "No one has a reaction when the shark comes up! I don't understand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.741,
    "endTime": 143.643,
    "text": "You're going to need a bigger boat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.643,
    "endTime": 145.812,
    "text": "Ah, you guys are going to need a lot more than a bigger boat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.812,
    "endTime": 148.681,
    "text": "You're going to need a better captain, because you're a wimp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.681,
    "endTime": 150.049,
    "text": "They're looking kinda nervous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.049,
    "endTime": 151.751,
    "text": "I bet you he's going to be the first one to die."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.751,
    "endTime": 153.31900000000002,
    "text": "The shark's getting closer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.319,
    "endTime": 155.188,
    "text": "There she is. Is there only one shark?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.188,
    "endTime": 156.22099999999998,
    "text": "Like it's 'the' shark?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.222,
    "endTime": 157.223,
    "text": "We'll call her Bessie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.058,
    "endTime": 161.194,
    "text": "Literally went like 'blaaaaow!' Destroyed it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.362,
    "endTime": 164.03,
    "text": "It's a pretty good shark. I believe it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.03,
    "endTime": 165.331,
    "text": "She's sinking you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.0,
    "endTime": 168.902,
    "text": "Right here… trying not to get…Oh, nope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.902,
    "endTime": 171.337,
    "text": "Somebody help him, somebody help him…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.337,
    "endTime": 173.206,
    "text": "He's kicking him with his…Really? Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.341,
    "endTime": 176.24200000000002,
    "text": "Ewp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.242,
    "endTime": 177.41,
    "text": "Not coming back from that..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.41,
    "endTime": 178.545,
    "text": "Uh-uh, uh-uh…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "Ewww."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 184.117,
    "text": "He's half in the mouth. Just writhing around."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.117,
    "endTime": 186.25099999999998,
    "text": "No music going on. Just like 'aaaaahhhh.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.252,
    "endTime": 188.02100000000002,
    "text": "Doesn't all the extra shit that the shark is eating"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.021,
    "endTime": 189.45399999999998,
    "text": "mess up the taste of the humans?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.455,
    "endTime": 192.125,
    "text": "No one has peeped a word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.125,
    "endTime": 193.86,
    "text": "I think his friend probably should have helped him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.86,
    "endTime": 196.46200000000002,
    "text": "You're right! He could have at least threw something at him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.462,
    "endTime": 197.297,
    "text": "Like, 'Stop!'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.297,
    "endTime": 199.732,
    "text": "It's seem as though that you don't die"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.732,
    "endTime": 200.767,
    "text": "on the first bite."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.767,
    "endTime": 203.936,
    "text": "He almost just like slid into the mouth very slowly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.937,
    "endTime": 205.77200000000002,
    "text": "He was literally just like, 'Oh no…'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.706,
    "endTime": 208.607,
    "text": "Yeah, I mean my heart is kinda beating."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.608,
    "endTime": 210.41,
    "text": "I think this plot doesn't make any sense."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.41,
    "endTime": 211.411,
    "text": "I felt no emotion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.411,
    "endTime": 212.812,
    "text": "I feel like everyone was just kind of like…"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.713,
    "endTime": 214.74699999999999,
    "text": "I still don't get it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.747,
    "endTime": 216.91600000000003,
    "text": "I don't think a shark is like on a mission"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.916,
    "endTime": 218.751,
    "text": "to attack a certain group of people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.751,
    "endTime": 219.953,
    "text": "People of America!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.953,
    "endTime": 221.621,
    "text": "If you don't want big sharks like that,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.621,
    "endTime": 222.422,
    "text": "recycle,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.422,
    "endTime": 224.057,
    "text": "don't put plastics in the ocean,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.057,
    "endTime": 225.558,
    "text": "don't put antibiotics in the ocean."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.558,
    "endTime": 226.392,
    "text": "This is what happened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.392,
    "endTime": 227.627,
    "text": "That's what 'Jaws' is about."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.627,
    "endTime": 229.095,
    "text": "Alright, we got this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.095,
    "endTime": 235.501,
    "text": "You're going to need a bigger boat."
  }
]